<article id="post-759281" class="post-759281 digital-library type-digital-library status-publish has-post-thumbnail hentry category-architecture-and-hardware issue-august-2024 section-news">

			
<header class="article-header article-header--default">
	<div class="article-header__inner container">
		<div class="article-header__section"><a href="https://cacm.acm.org/section/news/">News</a></div>
		<div class="article-header__topic-and-issue-section">
			<span class="article-header__topic">
			<a href="https://cacm.acm.org/category/architecture-and-hardware/">Architecture and Hardware</a>			</span>
			<span class="article-header__issue-section">
							</span>
		</div>
		<h1 class="article-header__title">Spinning Electrons to Attain Low-Power Computing</h1>
					<div class="article-header__subtitle"><p>Previously neglected materials are being used to spin up novel computing devices.</p>
</div>
		
		<div class="article-header__meta">
			<div class="article-header__byline">
				By <a href="https://cacm.acm.org/author/chris-edwards/" title="Posts by Chris Edwards" class="author url fn" rel="author">Chris Edwards</a>			</div>
			<div class="article-header__posted-on">
				<span class="posted-on">Posted <time datetime="2024-07-30T17:43:00-04:00">Jul 30 2024</time></span>			</div>
		</div>

			<figure class="article-header__figure">
			<div class="image-wrapper image-wrapper--widescreen"><img width="1024" height="576" src="https://cacm.acm.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/071524.News_.Spinning-Electrons.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full" alt="swirling beams surround a ball of light, illustration" loading="eager" decoding="async" srcset="https://cacm.acm.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/071524.News_.Spinning-Electrons.jpg 2140w, https://cacm.acm.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/071524.News_.Spinning-Electrons.jpg?resize=300,169 300w, https://cacm.acm.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/071524.News_.Spinning-Electrons.jpg?resize=768,432 768w, https://cacm.acm.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/071524.News_.Spinning-Electrons.jpg?resize=1024,576 1024w, https://cacm.acm.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/071524.News_.Spinning-Electrons.jpg?resize=1536,864 1536w, https://cacm.acm.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/071524.News_.Spinning-Electrons.jpg?resize=2048,1152 2048w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></div>		</figure>

		<div class="article-header__share">
			
